Add this line near the top of the template's CLAUDE.md, right after the "# CLAUDE.md" heading:

```
@devsoul.md
```

The hook in .claude/settings.json fetches devsoul.md from GitHub on first prompt,
then this import makes Claude load it into every session.

If the template repo already has a .claude/settings.json, merge the hooks block
into the existing file rather than replacing it.
